2. Chan, W. Kim and Rene’e Mauborgne (2005). Blue Ocean Strategy: From Strategy to Practice, California Management Review, spring, 105-121.
3. Eisenhardt, K., and D. Sull. (2001). Strategy as simple rules. Harvard Business Review, January 2001: 106-116.
